<!-- Game Description Table -->

<table class="tablestyle" id="table14" cellspacing="4" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td class="sectional">
		
<!-- Game Description Header -->
		
		<table class="headertable" id="table15" cellspacing="2" cellpadding="2">
			<tr>
				<td class="headercell">
				<img border="0" src="../../../images/headers/gamedes.jpg" width="240" height="33"></td>
			</tr>
		</table>

<!-- Game Description Sectional -->

<table border="0" width="100%" id="table16" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
			<br>R Rock'n'Riders is a snowboard game in which the player can control 6 different characters (all members of a rock band) in a near future world in which they are wanted by the law ('cause the rock is againts the law in that time) and they have to complete each level of the game descending it on a snowboard and getting some musical instruments that the other members of the band give him. If the player reach the level without the instruments he will have to replay it.
                  <br><br>The goal of the game is to reach L.A. to play in a concert with the band.
                  <br><br>In the level the player will encounter the people that will give the instruments and the enemies (the policeman) that will try to get the instruments from him.
                  <br><br>You must complete the level before the time limit or the game will end.
                  <br><br>MAIN CHARACTERS:
                  <br>- Chisato: Snowboard, guitar
                  <br>- Kyoji: Snowboard, guitar
                  <br>- Ellemo: Snowboard,microphone
                  <br>- O-jiro: Snowboard,drum
                  <br>- Yasumicha'n: Snowboard,bass
                  <br>- Kiyoshi: Snowboard,guitar
                  <br><br>The limited edition comes with a bonus disc that features photo galleries of all the members of the rock band.				  
                  <br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;<u>Manufacturer's description:</u><br>
			<br>Only band that was formed for the game [R] member, Kiyoshi, Chisato, a fusion of music and sport a big success in the motif of the other characters Yamamoto Yasushi 3D action. Sea, desert, snowy mountains, brilliant technique to determine the course gallantly Bodoraidingu San Francisco 4, let's gather scattered sound stage.
			<br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;<u>Features:</u><br>
			<ul><li>Third person perspective</li>
			<li>2D graphics</li>
			<li>Cartoon graphics</li>
			<li>SCI-FI, Futuristic, Music & Snowboard themes.</li></ul></td>
	</tr>
	</table>
	       	</td>
     </tr>
</table>  

